能&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt; &lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;60 年前：&lt;/strong&gt; 1966 年世界杯前几天，足球界最珍贵的奖杯消失了，一周后才被一只名叫 Pickles 的狗发现。这个混乱的传奇故事实际上&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/Lpi32yJ3EVaKXqkfMLPr41PgwEfDC3Qr9hdjLneWGjUKhBm2nN5BJy9QuCvzrGi899hu26s4phgGY_h6CQswIH3Z2R4prbnQ1s7dxZJdQQ9JB6AhNxfg16ol_068d30JuTXHBc4quMNYjYWXwzklXhzJ2XfHWIbbrxZnhipYEUswQ6Fh6nokfXAORP3Hjzw1SV4BogS2X5zS3QgTFNg1qOu80tIllvwRcQ4Fy7rZaHUTWDvfDUTDW7UvCNW1xNVPvHsS7pxJI6oOzT_GNKes_wdxhbRnhRymI-G10r0XtlCrQW9LcXoLJoTnJD3exIDUNgaNZc2Kxoqn3tkJzyjx-PdrxSMhLOCD-9fBUzm_A1fx9bf7l6yTDYcKu2OkMNDNWON6ClKikB1FhzT2dvlGCQrXDkwt1ojs3VIDoeiFRGJ2KWD5rsIjFd1Q_YXsIzPWGc6IrU7iFVOraFQusC0QmPoS2wi9OPQI2ekCkS2hTXLrd7KX7ALwBv7ZvhdOstxsCGXojmuX45PmCV-md2FFoAVih_D9zNcmqNdE/vMPo_s0l7w6reEbWqZnSB1iRdQAlYBKl/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="世界杯失踪的混乱一周"&gt;比其整洁的结局所暗示的还要奇怪&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;近 200 年前：&lt;/strong&gt;当工业革命袭击英国时，小说家将其剧变转化为有关工作、阶级和社会变革的故事。他们所捕捉到的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/g-hGThouayyBTeWabFi6hRWu5tTlgyRoilsHghH-kIpuXAD0itJhiKa2kjw4sb2BE6N2m3fF7tT5g2o9ypolBDy_fLxmpcL9qWQcRgHLaB68joil3bi6BHpo6UPNMj3FyJ7LzZI6942f3fb_H26TvYYxeVi3eBmljomDHxsSIhIE5CZk9oNJNwttmehx-K6x_Y9X1-07XaRhzGDp3Ipng0sRozFNjvxvRrE9salGYBDu5FE5BY7CMJH9z1k44v_q3IFSZJzu1QsQFjlZDJTy26oeJ7iYilRpc2YpaAmSuOROVBCbHU4RlLNpWSOLZ3L16fQ98I97X-8nSg1hyWjQIr9usEq_blIFtBzS7he7om6WZ20NTSyD5UN0M36mlUJQ2gSFlqqDmIgfcdH_gpJOLWEYDOTZuutRJIcjT-tJ_mu30hBhou6Vhl_ZHKsfDaR5ZgVsF8uCg5YSLlDp39irh64OM17Go3d_48tCbtVpv3fvjmSdFs0CSoVxgzg7K8kj9jtmDrkPTR4porA1f_KmELvaOR4vwcG1Pa1MJQ/C_jHsqsWLct9C8Ckz-8CP4SZcXbLgFBV/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="人工智能革命的最佳指南可能是维多利亚时代的小说"&gt;可能是我们现在对人工智能革命最接近的指南&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure style="margin: 20px 0;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/YoPRMKAIDk37UVDkAWzromIiRQ1d8ZZbG0fDJe_6eSPDZKwRyaPQVynqLIX6EfrOkCz4sbwbrJfjJUtptZyNgBhRcSWmCfZWaAZGBwVJcVtIoedg0IXkYgljRqaKhZXCGeIdka-csa5MH_DSvxdXtzMGju62KEF0hJRY20Px2TM39iUEpanJPoAxbSmmpXrCxpNa2fKqu05spi6d93CbUtzOnJpI4-RnpxUdpTxC_PSl6stl3A2Sq7xoVrzu371kiT7ldKBWIT20Vf7gW2KVOuMfDznSeRjo_2ZOMOiKtj279MqAS7SVxQGYaWm50_c8Ki4jDOJVd8DvxNAM1T5BvltUpMO3XISYu0EBCkwqE-yz9G3L2-GROwXLCGvuGtiEkA7TJzvSguEUu8U7H9uUeCf_f80FHVpnj8I/MJFv2HPI8Vo8Z-Eko4sxnFYXD5WOiwD9/19" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/izeA0Cdft83s/v0/-999x-999.gif" alt="" width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="替代" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/izeA0Cdft83s/v0/-999x-999.gif" style="width: 100%; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4; font-style: italic;"&gt; &lt;em style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4; font-style: italic;"&gt;Irene Suosalo 为彭博社绘制的插图&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;h2 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;对话开始者&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;耐心的强人正在赢得这场持久战。&lt;/strong&gt;像弗拉基米尔·普京和习近平这样的领导人几十年来一直严格&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/thzhZ0vKb8CvIcZebb8piCORhqO1KaLMn98Dsgf1tk8unj6MtozCXgBUz9UhguODe-i6HyBw9CDSKRAP0pXN2Y7G5QnJ1MGQvaS7tzRi49w0psGVDrZBPMJIVOqbr8i4kwSDkH2Qsq0ZKBttIj4nJbt9nnyzwSxhBZ45a6nHv7j4lk3Dlgqj2Y1PCiXcbqRuGi-3SMrDZQ4qoygFhw20yxr4R0bRLLEvv3eweWHudNHLKEeBSN_MxzMFOxeKBbjySGz2wwxckj0f4v9gN6muQhUY9CNKJwVA9mpcKo04vEUiMFsbspSCwBzeMSB4dRe6XINeC_siRERvZDfQr6mE3Tk51oK40Dz6ypM6iiS08dKhLSW0rqNh0dOwAJp8nDn70P6ph8xxlpC9ywqYo1DfHhea